categories-append     graphics
license         PSF
platforms       darwin
maintainers     nomaintainer
description     Python bindings to the Tk widget set
long_description \
    ${description}

homepage        https://docs.python.org/library/tkinter.html

python.versions 26 27 31 32 33 34 35 36 37

